      • string_with_space

        public java.lang.String string_with_space(java.lang.String string_with_no_space)
        Some syllabus has space, but due to processing has no more space. In this case, we need to get back its original word with space.
        Parameters:
        string_with_no_space - - string that has been processed and has no space
        Returns:
        string_with_space - string that has been processed and added space. if it's original word has no space, then the input word will be returned (base case)
